{"tid":2072602,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國安法草案】彈出彈入 8月先立","createTime":"2020-06-20T16:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T03:01:21.000Z","uid":206466,"like":7,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfc604457052f4e68f4beecdfb0cbf5461f7e9f","tid":2072602,"uid":206466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EWpTEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EWpTEh.jpg&h=d65367cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【國安法草案】栗戰書：符合憲法和基本法精神　最快 8 月通過草案<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委今日 ( 20 日) 閉幕，新華社亦於傍晚公布人大常委法工委草案說明。新華社再於晚上刊出人大常委委員長栗戰書於閉幕會上的演說內容，栗戰書就會議初次審議港區國安法草案作總結，指常委會組成人員都認為法律草案符合憲法和香港基本法精神，預料最快 8 月通過草案，並列入《基本法》附件三，同日由港府公布實施。<br />\n<br />\n報道來源：立場新聞"},{"pid":"6357b7861735eff8b62a980e9012bdf1e0978df5","tid":2072602,"uid":106252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ca2db9aa70cf3170296b51624879d3c96f497a","tid":2072602,"uid":167928,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"北戴河會議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b5dfce3cd0cc83c2204c494661aaaee170a04d","tid":2072602,"uid":206466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03ca2db9aa70cf3170296b51624879d3c96f497a","tid":2072602,"uid":167928,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"北戴河會議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c4f8b359c4639584d3d539918a23953b9e8be6","tid":2072602,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"借個位 立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072298</a> <i